 115:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** /** @defgroup FLASH_Private_Functions
 116:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****   * @{
 117:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****   */
 118:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** 
 119:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** /**
 120:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** @code  
 121:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  
 122:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  This driver provides functions to configure and program the Flash memory of all STM32F10x devices,
 123:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  including the latest STM32F10x_XL density devices. 
 124:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** 
 125:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  STM32F10x_XL devices feature up to 1 Mbyte with dual bank architecture for read-while-write (RWW) 
 126:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****     - bank1: fixed size of 512 Kbytes (256 pages of 2Kbytes each)
 127:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****     - bank2: up to 512 Kbytes (up to 256 pages of 2Kbytes each)
 128:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  While other STM32F10x devices features only one bank with memory up to 512 Kbytes.
 129:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** 
 130:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  In version V3.3.0, some functions were updated and new ones were added to support
 131:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  STM32F10x_XL devices. Thus some functions manages all devices, while other are 
 132:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  dedicated for XL devices only.
 133:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  
 134:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  The table below presents the list of available functions depending on the used STM32F10x devices. 
 135:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****       
 136:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    ***************************************************
 137:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    * Legacy functions used for all STM32F10x devices *
 138:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    ***************************************************
