 851:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****   * @brief  Programs a half word at a specified address.
 852:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****   * @note   This function can be used for all STM32F10x devices.
 853:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****   * @param  Address: specifies the address to be programmed.
 854:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****   * @param  Data: specifies the data to be programmed.
